hy kbIr! prmwqmw dw ismrn C`fx dw hI ieh nqIjw hY ik mnu`K swrI aumr inrw t`br hI pwldw rihMdw hY,
(t`br dI ^wqr) jgq dy DMDy krdw (qy, ijMd dy swQI prmwqmw qoN ivCiVAw rih ky) Aw^r Awqmk mOqy mr jWdw hY (ies Awqmk mOq qoN) koeI irSqydwr bcwx-jogw nhIN huMdw ]106]
