hy kbIr! ("rwmu n CofIAY, qnu Dnu jwie q jwau" nhIN qW) rwm-nwm C`fx dw hI ieh nqIjw hY ik (mUrK) iesqRI sIqlw dI vrq r`KdI iPrdI hY[
