hy kbIr! Fol moiFAW qy r`K ky mYN (vjWdw iPirAw hW qy) swrw jgq gwihAw hY (mYN pu`Cdw iPirAw hW ik d`so, BweI! ies rwj-Bwg, mhl-mwVIAW, swk-sMbMDI ivcoN koeI qoV inBx vwlw swQI BI iksy ny vyiKAw hY, pr iksy ny hwmI nhIN BrI)
