(ieh mmqw dI jyvVI koeI swDwrn ijhw jkV-bMd nhIN huMdw) hy kbIr! (prmwqmw dy ismrn qoN KuMJ ky mwieAw-moh dI r`sI ivc b`Jy hoieAW dw hwl jy qUM smJxw hY qW vyK ik mOq isr auqy Aw A`pVdI hY) jIvwqmw (srIr ivcoN) inklx qy huMdw hY, srIr (Awqmw dy ivCuVn qy) Fih-FyrI hox vwlw huMdw hY, iPr vI moh dI jyvVI nwl b`Jw hoieAw jIv sYxqW nwl hI (ipCly sMbMDIAW nUM) smJWdw hY,
